Content.Text:
<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
Hummm... isn't this a little spitfire
of a spell, eh? Very difficult!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
<MYNAME>, could you leave me alone today?
I'm very busy with my magic practice.
I want to hang out with you

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
You dare to stand in MY way, <MYNAME>?
YOU dare? The impudence!
<PAGE>
I don't have time to play with you right
now. Go on, out! Or do you want to be a
frog?

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
Argh! Now I've totally forgotten the
spell I was trying to remember. This
is your fault, <MYNAME>!
<PAGE>
You little imbecile!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
Thank you, <MYNAME>. I will definitely
repay you for this.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
Check it out! I've completed the new
spell!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
This is all thanks to you, <MYNAME>. If
you hadn't left me alone back there then
I would surely have failed.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
Here's a present for you. Put out your
hand.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
This is just a little thank you. Don't
hold back, just take it and enjoy! Bye-
bye now!
